title: The total package! Res Lease in . 3 Beds, 3 Baths
posting_body: Tour this superb BRAND NEW 3-bedroom, 2-and-a-half bathroom home in the Addison neighborhood of Austin TX today!
You'll enjoy everything this lovely home has to offer, with its incredible green areas that are perfect for gardening or exercising, to its spacious rooms that allow in tons of natural light.

When you walk around, you will find the perfect area for an office space, and fall in love with the wonderful living room that features wood grain flooring and a ceiling fan to help keep the house cool on the hot Texas days.

This home also boasts an elegant kitchen with white cabinetry, plenty of counter and storage space, a pantry, and stainless steel appliances, just waiting for your home cook to create some beautiful meals.
Tour and apply to this one and be the FIRST person to live in this beautiful home before it’s gone!
